my Familia, don't I?

240
00:10:53,013 --> 00:10:54,879
Anyway, here,
these are for you.

241
00:10:54,979 --> 00:10:55,979
Huh?

242
00:10:56,079 --> 00:10:57,646
Oh no! I can't take those!

243
00:10:57,746 --> 00:11:00,813
Just consider it a small
token of my many thanks.

244
00:11:00,913 --> 00:11:02,579
And an open door to
keep doing business

245
00:11:02,679 --> 00:11:03,713
with my Familia.

246
00:11:03,813 --> 00:11:05,779
Uh... thanks a lot.

247
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:08,413
[MIACH]
You take care, Bell.

248
00:11:08,513 --> 00:11:10,113
Hm.

249
00:11:14,746 --> 00:11:18,013
[HEPHAISTOS]
Um, how long do you
plan to keep doing that?

250
