annoying distraction.

252
00:11:29,113 --> 00:11:30,913
(Hephaistos sighs)

253
00:11:31,013 --> 00:11:32,913
(Crowd gasps)

254
00:11:33,013 --> 00:11:34,913
[HEPHAISTOS]
