258
00:11:41,213 --> 00:11:43,946
I know it's a lot
to ask... but I‐

259
00:11:44,046 --> 00:11:46,013
Come up with
the money first...

260
00:11:46,113 --> 00:11:48,313
and then
we can talk.

261
00:11:48,913 --> 00:11:49,846
Ah!

262
00:11:49,946 --> 00:11:51,079
(Hephaistos groans)

263
00:11:51,179 --> 00:11:53,146
[HESTIA]
