I beg you!

265
00:11:56,846 --> 00:11:59,179
Oh, my...

266
00:12:00,746 --> 00:12:01,913
[HEPHAISTOS]
Listen Hestia,

267
00:12:02,013 --> 00:12:03,213
I don't know what
you're doing exactly,

268
00:12:03,313 --> 00:12:04,946
