knock it off?

269
00:12:05,046 --> 00:12:06,479
[HESTIA]
Ugh. It's called groveling.

270
00:12:06,579 --> 00:12:09,046
Takemikazuchi says it's the
ultimate strategy

271
00:12:09,146 --> 00:12:10,446
for asking a favor.

272
00:12:10,546 --> 00:12:12,613
[HEPHAISTOS]
Ugh, he's always
getting into things

273
00:12:12,713 --> 00:12:13,979
where he doesn't belong.

274
00:12:14,079 --> 00:12:15,246
Tell me...

275
00:12:15,346 --> 00:12:17,446
Why do you want this
so badly, Hestia?

276
00:12:17,546 --> 00:12:19,746
[HESTIA]
I am trying to
help Bell, okay?

277
00:12:19,846 --> 00:12:21,979
He's been so
different lately!

278
00:12:22,079 --> 00:12:23,846
He's got a single
goal on his mind.

279
00:12:23,946 --> 00:12:25,379
He's running straight
towards it

280
00:12:25,479 --> 00:12:27,746
and will stop at
absolutely nothing!

281
00:12:27,846 --> 00:12:29,546
And it's a dangerous path.

282
00:12:29,646 --> 00:12:32,646
That's why I want to
give him strength!

283
00:12:32,746 --> 00:12:35,413
(Crying)
He needs a weapon
that can clear the way!

284
00:12:36,479 --> 00:12:38,213
All I want to do
is help him...

285
00:12:38,313 --> 00:12:41,146
[HESTIA]
and do whatever I can
to support him.

286
00:12:41,246 --> 00:12:43,446
[HESTIA]
Even though I'm his goddess,

287
