Oh, okay.

356
00:15:06,646 --> 00:15:09,379
Syr took the day off so she'd be
able to go see the festival.

357
00:15:09,479 --> 00:15:11,713
In fact, she was so
excited about going...

358
00:15:11,813 --> 00:15:14,513
